hadiths[95]{hadithnumber,text}:
4064,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''jab tum apna kutta chhodo to Allah ka naam lekar chhodo , agar wo tumharey liye pakad ley aur tum usey zinda pa lo to usey zibeh karo, agar tum usey is haal mein paao ke usney (shikar ko) qatl kar diya aur use khaya nahin to phir usey kha lo , aur agar usney kha liya hai to phir na khaao kyonkey usney apney liye pakda hai, agar tum apney kuttey ke sath doosra kutta dekho aur shikar ko murda paao to usey mat khaao kyonkey tum nahin jantey ke un dono mein se kis ne qatl kiya, aur jab tum teer chalaao to Allah ka naam lekar chalaao. phir agar wo shikar tumhen eik roz baad miley aur tum is mein sirf apney teer hi ka nishan dekho to phir agar chaho to kha lo, aur agar tum usey pani mein dooba hua paao to usey mat khaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
4065,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham (shikar ke liye) sadhaaey huey kuttey chhodtey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney jo tumharey liye pakda hai kha lein.'' maine arz kiya, agar wo maar dalen? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar-che wo maar dalen.'' maine arz kiya : ham mea'raaz (paron ke baghair teer) phainktey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo nauk ki taraf se shikar mein ghus jaey to kha lein aur agar usey chorai waley hissey ki taraf se lagey aur wo qatl ho jaey to usey mat khaeyn, kyonkey wo chot lagney se mara hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4066,"Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! ham ehle-kitab ki sarzameen par rihaaish pazeer (thehre hue) hain, kya ham unke bartanon mein kha liya karen, aur isi sarzameen par main apni kamaan aur apney ghair sadhaaey huey aur sadhaaey huey kuttey ke zariey shikar karta hun, to merey liye kya durust hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne jo ehle-kitab ke bartanon ka zikr kya hai to agar tumhen unke ilawa bartan muyassar aa jaeyn to phir un mein mat khaao , aur agar muyassar na ayen to phir unhen dho kar un mein kha lo . aur tum ne apni kamaan se jo shikar kiya hai agar tum ne is par Allah ka naam zikr kiya hai to kha lo, aur tum ne jo apney sadhaaey huey kuttey ke sath shikar kiya hai aur Allah ka naam zikr kiya hai to kha lo aur tum ne apney ghair sadhaaey huey kuttey se jo shikar kiya hai agar usey zibeh kar lo to kha lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4067,"Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum ne apna teer (shikar par) phenka aur wo (shikar) teri nazron se ojhal ho gaya, phir tum ne usey pa liya to agar wo badbudar nahin hua to usey kha saktey ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
4068,"Hazrat Abu Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us shakhs ke barey mein , jo teen roz baad apna shikar paata hai, farmaya : ''agar wo badbudar nahin hua to usey kha ley.'' rawahu Muslim."
4069,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! yahan kuchh aisey log hain jo naey naey musalman huey hain, wo hamarey paas gosht latey hain, ham nahin jantey ke aaya wo is par Allah ka naam letey hain ya nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Allah ka naam lo aur khaao.'' Bukhari."
4070,"Hazrat Abu-Tufail ( Aamir bin Waasila ( bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tumhen koi khas chiz ata farmaee? unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein koi khas aisi chiz ata nahin farmaee jo aapney deegar logon ko na batai ho. albatta ye chiz hai jo ke meri talwaar ke niyaam mein hai, unhoney eik saheefa (kitab) nikala is mein darj tha : ''ghair Allah ke liye zibeh karney waley par Allah lanat karey, zamin ke nishan (hudood) chori karney waley par Allah lanat karey.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jisney zamin ke nishaanaat (milkiyati hudood) badal daley (Allah is par lanat farmaey)'' apney walid par lanat karney waley par Allah lanat karey aur bid'ati shakhs ko panah deney waley shakhs par Allah lanat karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
4071,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham kal dushman se mulaqat karney waley hain, jabkey hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahin, kya ham sar-kandey ke sath zibeh kar lein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo khoon baha dey aur jis par Allah ka naam liya jaey usey khaao, (jabkey) daant aur nakhun ke sath zibeh karna durust nahin, aur main tumhen uskey mutalliq tafseelaat batata hun daant haddi hai, aur raha nakhun to wo habshiyon ki chhuriyaan hain.'' (kuffar par hamla karney ke baad) ham ko oont aur bakriyan milin , un mein se eik oont bhag khada hua to eik aadmi ne is par eik teer chalaya aur usey rok liya , is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''in janwaron mein bhi wehshi janwaron ki tarah bhagney waley hotey hain, un mein se jo be qabu ho jaey to tum uskey sath isi tarah kiya karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4072,"Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unki bakriyan thi jo salaa pahad par char rahi thin, hamari eik londi ne bakriyon mein se eik bakri ko marney ke qarib dekha to usney eik pathar toda aur uskey sath usey zibeh kar diya, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aapney unhen uskey khaney ka hukm farmaya. Bukhari."
4073,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne her chiz par ehsan karna farz kar diya hai, jab tum qatl karo to achhey tareeqey se qatl karo. jab tum zibeh karo to achhey tareeqey se zibeh karo, tum mein se her eik apni chhuri tez kar ley aur apney zabiha ko aaram pahunchaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
4074,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi chopaey ya kisi aur chiz ko baandh kar qatl karney se mana farmaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
4075,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us shakhs par lanat farmaai jo kisi zi-rooh chiz ko baandh kar nishane-bazi karey. muttafaq aleh.
4076,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi zi-rooh chiz ko (nishane-bazi ke liye) hadaf na banaao.'' rawahu Muslim.
4077,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chehrey par maarney aur chehrey ko daaghney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim."
4078,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik gadhey ke paas se guzrey jiskey chehrey ko daaghaa gaya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us shakhs par lanat farmaai jisney isey dagh diya.'' rawahu Muslim."
4079,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Abdullah bin Ubai Talha ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar gaya ta ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey ghati den (khajoor chabaa kar is ke taaloo mein laga den), maine aap ko dekha ke aap ke haath mein dagh laganey wala aala tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey sath sadqe ke oonton ko nishan laga rahey they. muttafaq aleh."
4080,"Hazrat Hisham bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) , Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap baadey mein they, maine aap ko dekha ke aap bakriyon ko nishan laga rahey they, raawi bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke unhoney kaha : aap un (bakriyon) ke kanon par nishan laga rahey they. muttafaq aleh."
4081,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! bataeyn ke ham mein se kisi ko shikar mil jaey aur uskey paas chhuri na ho to kya wo usey pathar aur lathi ke kinarey se zibeh kar sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khoon bahaao jiskey sath chaho, aur Allah ka naam lo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4082,"Hazrat Abu Ushraa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya zibeh sirf halaq aur seeney ke baalai (upri) hissey (labbaa) par chhuri chalaney se hi hota hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum ne uski raan par zakhm lagaya to bhi terey liye kafi hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne farmaya : ye kisi girey padey janwer ke zibeh karney ka tariqa hai. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye zarurat ke tehat hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4083,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kisi kuttey ya baaz ko sadhaayaa , phir tum ne usey Allah ka naam lekar chhoda to usney jo tumharey liye mehfooz rakha usey kha.'' maine arz kiya, agar wo maar dey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab usney usey maar diya aur is mein se kuchh na khaya to wo usney tumharey liye hi mehfooz rakha hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4084,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main shikar par teer phainktaa hun aur agley roz main is mein apna teer dekhta hun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhen yaqin ho gaya ke tumharey hi teer ne usey maara hai aur tum ne is mein kisi darindey ka nishan na dekha to phir khaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4085,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamen majusiyon ke kuttey ke shikar se rok diya gaya. rawahu Tirmizi."
4086,"Hazrat Abu Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham musafir log hain, ham yahood aur Nasara aur majusiyon ke paas se guzartey hain, hamein unke bartan hi mayyassar hotey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum unke ilawa na paao to unhen pani ke sath dho lo phir un mein khaao piyo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4087,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Halab apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isaiyon ke khaney ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, aur eik riwayat mein hai : eik aadmi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke baaz khaanon se main ijtinab (bachta) karta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney dil mein koi khaljaan mehsus na karo ke is main tum ne esaiyon ki mushaabihat ikhtiyar ki hai.'' (kyonkey wo bhi apney ilawa kisi ka khana nahin khatey.) rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4088,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujassame ke khaney se mana farmaya hai, aur ye wo hai jisey baandh kar teer maarey jaeyn. rawahu Tirmizi."
4089,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz darindon mein se her kuchli (se shikar karney) waley aur parindon mein se her panjey (se shikar karney) waley, paaltu gadhey ke gosht sey, baandh kar teer andazi kiye janey waley aur ''khleesa'' ke khaney se aur jang mein giraftar honey wali hamila aurat se waza' hamal se pehley jima (sambhog) karney se mana farmaya. Muhammad bin Yahya bayan kartey hain, Abu Aasim sey, mujassame ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : kisi perindey ya kisi chiz ko baandh ke is par teer andazi ki jaey, aur unsey, khleesa ke barey mein puchha gaya to farmaya , koi shakhs bhediye ya darindey se uska shikar chhudaaey aur wo uskey zibeh karney se qabl uskey haath mein mar jaey. rawahu Tirmizi."
4090,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shetan ke shareeta se mana farmaya hai, ibne-Esa ne izafa naqal kiya hai, ye (shareeta) wo zabiha hai ke uski jild kaat di jaey aur uski ragein na kaati jaeyn, phir usey chhod diya jaey yahan tak ke wo mar jaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4091,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''janeen (pet ke bachchey) ki maa ka zibeh karna uska zibeh karna hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi.
4092,Aur Imam Tirmizi ne usey Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
4093,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham oontni , gaaey aur bakri zibeh kartey hain aur ham unke pet mein bachcha paatey hain, to kya ham usey phenk den ya usey kha lein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar chaho to kha lo, kyonkey uski maa ko zibeh karna uska zibeh karna hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4094,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi chidiyaa ya us se ooper (chhotey ya badey) perindey ko nahaq qatl kiya to Allah uskey qatl ke mutalliq us se puchheyga, arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! uska haq kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey zibeh karey aur phir usey kha ley, aur wo uska sar kaat kar usey mat phenkey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Nasai aur Darmi."
4095,"Hazrat Abu Waqid Leeshi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to ehle Madina oonton ke kohan kaat liya kartey they dunbon ki chakkiyaan kaat liya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo hissey zinda janwer se kaat liya jaey to wo (kataa hua hissa) murdar hai, usey na khaya jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4096,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar , bano Harisa ke aadmi se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Uhad ki eik ghaati mein oontni charaaya karta tha, usney oontni mein maut ke aasaar dekhey to usney usey zibeh karney ke liye kuchh na paya , chunanche usney eik meekh li aur uskey seeney ke ooper ke hissey mein maar diya yahan tak ke uska khoon baha diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya to aapney usey khaney ka hukm farmaya. aur Maalik ki riwayat mein hai ke usney tez lakdi ke sath usey zibeh kiya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Maalik."
4097,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne tamam samandari janwer bani-Adam ke liye halal kiye hain.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
4098,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne rewad ki hifazat waley kuttey aur shikari kuttey ke ilawa koi aur kutta rakha to uskey amal se rozaana do qirat kami ki jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4099,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne rewad ki hifazat waley kuttey ya shikari ya kheti ki hifazat waley kuttey ke siwa koi aur kutta rakha to uskey ajr se rozaana eik qirat kam kiya jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4100,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey maarney ka hamein hukm farmaya yahan tak ke aurat jangal se apney kuttey ke sath aati to ham us (kuttey) ko bhi qatl kar detey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey maarney se mana farmaya , aur farmaya : ''tum do nuqton waley siyah kuttey ko qatl karo. kyonkey wo shetan hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4101,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shikari kuttey ya bakriyon ya rewad ki hifazat waley kuttey ke siwa deegar kutton ko maarney ka hukm farmaya. muttafaq aleh.
4102,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar kuttey Allah Taala ki makhluq na hotey to main un sab ko qatl karney ka hukm farmata , tum un mein se intehai siyah ko qatl karo.'' Abu-Dawud, Darmi. aur Imam Tirmizi aur Imam Nasai ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jo ghar waley shikari kuttey, kheti baadi ki ya bakriyon ki hifazat waley kuttey ke siwa koi kutta paaltey hain, unke amal mein se rozaana eik qirat kam kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Darmi, Tirmizi aur Nasai."
4103,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaupaaon ke darmiyan ladaai karaney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4104,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''darindon mein se kuchli waley janwer khana haram hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4105,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darindon mein se kuchli waley her janwer aur parindon mein se panjey (se shikar karney) waley her perindey (ke khaney) se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim."
4106,"Hazrat Abu Solba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ka gosht haram qarar diya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4107,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz paaltu gadhon ke gosht se mana farmaya aur ghodon ke gosht ki ijazat farmaey. muttafaq aleh.
4108,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik jangli gadhaa dekha aur usey shikar kar liya , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas uskey gosht mein se kuchh baqi hai? ''unhoney arz kiya : hamarey paas uski taang hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se wo taang lekar usey tanaawul farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
4109,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne marruz-zohraan ke paas eik khargosh ko daudaayaa , main usey pakad kar Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley aaya, unhoney usey zibeh kiya aur uska koolha aur uski dono raanein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejein to aapney unhen qubul farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
4110,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na main gau khata hun aur na usey haram qarar deta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
4111,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen bataya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur wo Khalid bin Waleed ki aur ibne-Abbas ki khaala hain, unhoney unke yahan bhuna hua saandaa paya , Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein wo pesh kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saandey se apna haath peechhey hata liya to Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya saandaa haram hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, lekin ye meri qom ke ilaqey mein paya nahin jata isliye main taba'i taur par isey napasand karta hun.'' Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine isey apney qarib kar liya aur kha liya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf dekh rahey they. muttafaq aleh."
4112,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko murgh ka gosht khatey huey dekha. muttafaq aleh."
4113,"Hazrat ibne-Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath , saat ghazawaat mein shirkat ki, ham aap ke sath tiddiyan khaya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
4114,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ghazwae-jaishul khabt mein shirkat ki, Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey Ameer muqarrar kiye gaey, ham shadeed bhook ka shikar ho gaey to samandar ne eik bahut badi murda machli bahar phenki, ham ne us jaisi machli kabhi nahin dekhi thi aur usey anbar ke naam se yad kya jata hai, ham ne usey nisf (aadhe) maah tak khaya. Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski haddiyon mein se eik haddi pakdi aur oont sawar uskey nichey se guzar gaya, jab ham wapis gaey to ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne tumhari taraf jo rizq nikala hai usey khaao aur agar tumharey paas is mein se kuchh hai to hamen bhi khilaao.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne is mein se kuchh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja to aapney usey khaya (khaaya). muttafaq aleh."
4115,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein makkhi gir jaey to wo usko achhi tarah pani mein ghota de-kar bahar phenkey, kyonkey uskey do mein se eik par mein shifaa jabkey doosrey mein bimari hai.'' Bukhari."
4116,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik chuhiyaa ghi mein gir kar mar gaee , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uskey mutalliq masla puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usko aur uskey Aas paas ke ghi ko phenk do aur baqiya (ghi) kha lo.'' Bukhari."
4117,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''saanpon ko qatl karo aur khas kar do lakeeron waley aur dam katey sanp ko qatl karo, kyonkey wo dono beenai khatam kar detey hain, aur hamal gira detey hain.'' Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is beech mein ke main eik sanp ko maarney ke liye uskey peechhey dauda to Abu-Lubaana (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey aawaz di : usey mat maaro maine kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saanpon ko maarney ka hukm farmaya hai, unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey baad gharon mein rehney walon ko maarney se mana farma diya tha. kyonkey wo un (gharon) ko abad rakhney waley hain. muttafaq aleh."
4118,"Hazrat Abu-Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, ham unke paas bethey huey they ke is beech mein ham ne unki chaarpai ke nichey koi aahat suni , ham ne dekha ke wo sanp tha, main usey qatl karney ke liye jaldi se utha jabkey Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padh rahey they, unhoney mujhey ishara kya ke main beth jaaun , main beth gaya, jab wo farigh huey to unhoney ghar main eik kamrey ki taraf ishara kiya aur farmaya : ye kamra dekh rahey ho? maine kaha : ji haan , unhoney farmaya is kamrey mein hamara eik nau-biyaahtaa nojawan tha, unhoney farmaya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khandaq ki taraf nikley , wo nojawan nisfun-nahar (din ka beech) ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat hasil karkey apni ehliya ke paas aa jaya karta tha, chunanche eik roz usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''apna aslaha sath ley jaao kyonkey mujhey tumharey mutalliq banu Qureza ka khatra hai.'' usney apna aslaha liya aur apney ghar ki taraf chal diya (jab wo ghar ke qarib pahuncha to) usney dekha ke uski ehliya darwazey par hai, usney ghairat mein aa kar uski taraf neza badhaya taake wo usey maarey , usney usey kaha apna neza roken aur kamrey mein ja kar dekhen ke wo kon si chiz hai jisney mujhey bahar nikalney par majbur kiya hai, wo dakhil hua to usney eik bahut badey azdahey ko kundli maarey zamin par dekha to usney neza is mein ghonp diya, phir wo bahar aa gaya aur usey ghar mein gaad diya sanp us (neze) par tadapne laga , malum nahin ho saka ke un dono mein se pehley kon mara , sanp ya wo nojawan? raawi bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se uska tazkira kiya aur ham ne arz kiya, Allah se dua farmaain ke wo usey hamarey liye zinda farma dey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney sathi ke liye maghfirat talab karo.'' phir farmaya : ''un gharon ke kuch makeen (rahne wale) hain, jab tum is tarah ki koi chiz dekho to usey teen baar ghar se nikalney par majbur karo agar wo chala jaey (to theek) warna usey maar do, kyonkey wo kafir hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Madina mein jin hain, jo Islam qubul kar chukey hain, jab tum un mein se koi chiz dekho to usey teen roz khabrdar karo, phir agar uskey baad bhi zahir ho to usey qatl kar do, kyonkey wo to shetan hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4119,"Hazrat Umme-Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne girgit maarney ka hukm farmaya , aur farmaya : ''wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke liye jalaai gaee aag bhadkaane ke liye phunkey maarta tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
4120,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne girgit ko maarney ka hukm farmaya aur uska naam fuwaisiq rakha. rawahu Muslim.
4121,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne pehli zarab mein girgit maar diya to uskey liye so neki likh di jati hai, aur dusri chot mein maarney waley ke liye us se kam aur teesri mein us se kam (neki likhi jati hai).'' rawahu Muslim."
4122,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''cheenti ne kisi Nabi (Alaihissalam) ko kaat liya to unhoney cheentiyon ke maskan (ghar) ko jala deney ka hukm farmaya to usey jala diya gaya, Allah Taala ne uski taraf ""wahi"" farmaee ke aap ko eik cheenti ne kaataa tha aur aapney eik aisi jamaat ko jala diya jo tasbih karti thi. muttafaq aleh."
4123,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab chuhiyaa ghi mein gir jaey, agar wo jaamid (jama hua) ho to us (chuhiyaa) ko aur uskey Aas paas waley ghi ko nikal kar phenk do , aur agar wo ghi pighli haalat mein ho to phir uskey qarib na jaao.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4124,Aur Imam Darmi ne usey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi.
4125,"Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath surkhaab ka gosht khaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4126,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gandagi khaney waley janwer ke khaney aur uskey doodh (peeney) se mana farmaya hai. Tirmizi. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghilazat khaney waley janwer ki sawari se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4127,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Shabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saandey ke gosht ko khaney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4128,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne billi ke gosht aur uski qeemat khaney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi.
4129,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke roz paaltu gadhon aur khachcharon ke gosht sey, kuchli waley darindon aur panjey se shikar karney waley parindon ke gosht se mana farmaya hai. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4130,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghodon , khachcharon aur gadhon ke gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4131,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ghazwae-khaibar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shirkat ki, yahood (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein) aaye aur unhoney shikayat ki ke logon ne unke phal daar darakhton se phal utaarney mein bahut jaldi ki hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! zimmiyon se nahaq maal lena halal nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4132,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey liye do murda chizen aur do khoon halal kiye gaey hain, do murdar machli aur tiddi hai, jabkey do khoon jigar aur tilli hain.'' rawahu Ahmed, ibne-Maja aur Dar-Qutni."
4133,"Hazrat Abu Zuber (Raziallahu anhu), Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis chiz ko samandar bahar (sahil ki taraf) phenk dey aur us se pani utar jaey to usey khaao , aur jo is mein mar jaey aur satah samandar par tairney lagey to usey mat khaao .''Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja. Imam Muhius Sunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aksar ka ye mauqif hai ke ye riwayat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf hai."
4134,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se tiddiyon ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo Allah ka Kasir lashkar hai, main usey na khata hun na haram qarar deta hun.'' Abu-Dawud, Muhius Sunnah ne farmaya : ye riwayat zaeef hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4135,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne murgh ko bura bhala kehney se mana farmaya hai, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo Namaz (ke waqt) ki ittilaa deta hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4136,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''murgh ko bura bhala na kaho, kyonkey wo Namaz ke liye bedaar karta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4137,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi-Laila bayan kartey hain, Abu-Laila (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghar mein sanp nikal aaye to usey kaho : ham tujhey Nuh aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke ehad ka hawala detey hain ke to hamein eza (takleef) na pahuncha. agar wo dobara nikley to usey qatl kar do.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4138,"Hazrat Ikrima , ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Ikrima ne kaha : main janta hun ke unhoney isey marfoo bayan kiya hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) saanpon ko maarney ka hukm farmaya kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney sanp ke intiqam ke khof se unhen chhod diya to wo ham mein se nahin.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4139,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab se hamari un (saanpon) se ladaai shuru hui hai ham ne un se suleh nahin ki, aur jisney dar ke peshe-nazar un mein se kisi (saanp) ko (maarey baghair) chhod diya to wo ham mein se nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4140,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her qism ke sanp ko qatl karo, aur jo shakhs unke intiqam se dar gaya wo mujh se nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4141,"Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham zam zam kunwey ki safai karna chahtey hain aur is mein chhotey chhotey sanp hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen maar dalney ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4142,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaandi ki salaakh ki misl (jaise) safed saanpon ke ilawa tamam saanpon ko maar dalo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein makkhi gir jaey to usey dubo dey , kyonkey uskey eik par mein bimari hai, jabkey doosrey mein shifa hai, wo apney is par ke zariey (girney sey) bachti hai jis mein bimari hai, isliye usey mukammal taur par dubo do.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4144,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab makkhi khaney mein gir jaey to usey dubo den , kyonkey uskey eik par mein zahar hai jabkey doosrey mein shifa hai, aur wo zahar waley par ko muqaddam rakhti hai aur shifa waley par ko muakhkhar.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4145,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar janwaron : cheenti , shehad ki makkhi , hud-hud aur latoorey ko maarney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
4146,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ehle jahiliyat kuchh chizen khaya kartey they aur kuchh chizen bator karaahat chhod diya kartey they, Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Nabi banakar bheja , apni kitab nazil farmaee, usney halal karda chizon ko halal aur apni haram karda chizon ko haram qarar diya, usney jin chizon ko halal kiya wo halal hai aur jin ko haram kiya wo haram hai, aur jis se khamoshi ikhtiyar ki to wo qabile pakad nahin, phir ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''farma dijiye ! meri taraf jo ""wahi"" ki gaee hai, main is mein khaney waley ke liye jo wo khata hai, murdar , behta hua khoon , khinzir ke gosht ke siwa koi aur chiz haram nahin paata.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4147,"Hazrat Zaahir Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke manadi karney waley ne ye aelan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen gadhon ke gosht se mana farmatey hain, main us waqt handiyon ke nichey aag jala raha tha, jin mein gadhon ka gosht tha. Bukhari."
4148,"Hazrat Abu Saulba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) marfoo riwayat bayan kartey hain : ''jinnon ki teen qismen hain : eik qism ye hai ke uskey par hain aur wo hawa mein udtey hain, eik qism saanpon aur kutton ki hai aur eik qism ye hai ke wo padaaw daltey hain, aur koochh kartey hain.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4149,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir Zabi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''ladkey ke paida honey par aqiqa hai, uski taraf se khoon bahaao (janwer zibeh karo)  aur us se takleef door karo (us ka sar mundaao aur usey nahlaao).'' Bukhari."
4150,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bachchey laye jatey to aap unke liye barkat ki dua farmatey, aur unhen ghati detey they. rawahu Muslim."
4151,"Hazrat Asma binte-Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Abdullah bin Zuber Makka mein merey pet mein they, unhoney kaha, maine usey qubaa mein janm diya, phir main usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laee to maine usey aap ki god mein rakh diya, phir aapney khajoor managaai usey chabaayaa aur apna luaabe-dahan laga kar usey uskey munh mein dala aur ghati di, phir uskey liye barkat ki dua farmaee. aur ye ( Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu)) Islam (hijrat ke baad Madina) mein paida honey waley pehley bachhey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4152,"Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''parindon ko unki jagahon par rehney do.'' (faal leney ke liye unhen na udaao) unhoney bayan kiya, aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri hai. aur unka nar ya mada hona tumharey liye Muzar nahin.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi. aur Nasai ki riwayat : ''ladkey ki taraf se. . . .'' aakhir tak hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur Nasai."
4153,"Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) , Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladka apney aqeeqe ke badley mein girwi hai, saatwen roz uski taraf se zibeh kiya jaey uska naam rakha jaey, aur uska sar moondaaya jaey.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai. lekin un dono (Abu-Dawood aur Nasai) ki riwayat mein (murtahin) ki jagah (رھینۃ) ke alfaz hain. aur Musnad Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein (ویسمّی) ki bajaey (ویدمّی) ke alfaz hain. aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne farmaya : lafz (ویسمّی) ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4154,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) , Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se eik bakri zibeh ki, aur farmaya : ''Fatima ! iska sar moond aur iskey baalon ke barabar chaandi sadqa kar.'' chunanche ham ne un baalon ka wazan liya to unka wazan eik dirham ya dirham se kam tha. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, iski sanad muttasil nahin, kyonkey Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain ki Ali bin abi Talib se mulaqat Sabit nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
4155,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se eik eik mendhey se aqeeqa kiya. Abu-Dawood. aur Nasai ki riwayat mein do do mendhon ka zikr hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai.
4156,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aqiqe ke barey mein masla puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ''uqooq'' ko pasand nahin karta.'' goya aapney ye naam napasand farmaya , aur farmaya : ''jis ke yahan bachcha paida ho aur wo uski taraf se zibeh karna pasand karey to wo ladkey ki taraf se do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf se eik bakri zibeh karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4157,"Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke kaan mein Namaz wali Azan di. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4158,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, daure-jahiliyat mein jab ham mein se kisi ke yahan ladka paida hota to wo bakri zibeh karta aur uskey sar par uska khoon lagata , aur jab Islam ka zuhoor hua to ham saatwen roz bakri zibeh kartey aur uska sar moondtey aur Zaafran lagatey they. Abu-Dawood. aur Rizeen ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : aur ham uska naam rakhtey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Rizeen."
